<title>SOUTH AFRICA: CDC issues fresh cautionary.</title>
<headline>CDC issues fresh cautionary.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Consolidated Diamond Corp Ltd on Thursday urged shareholders to exercise further caution in share dealings pending a further announcement.</p>
<p>It gave no further details in a cautionary announcement. The company first cautioned shareholders on January 21 and again on March 4.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27-11 482 1003</p>
